    [ 8948.249320] kworker/u16:18/933570 is trying to acquire lock:
    [ 8948.249812] ffff9b3de1591690 (sb_internal#2){.+.+}-{0:0}, at: find_free_extent+0x141e/0x1590 [btrfs]
